        "start": "0:00:58.12",
        "end": "0:01:08.8"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "text": "It's located here just north of one of those borders that's so messed up that it's not actually technically accurate to even call it a border because nobody really ever agreed it was a border.",
