    "instances": [
      {
        "adjustedStart": "0:01:24.88",
        "adjustedEnd": "0:01:26.68",
        "start": "0:01:24.88",
        "end": "0:01:26.68"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "text": "It's also a non military zone flanked on two sides by much military and it's also supposed to be temporary but as of yet isn't.",
