        "start": "0:01:53.04",
        "end": "0:01:54.36"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 28,
    "text": "Those shenanigans got started really, really early because Cyprus spent time under control by the Greeks and the Persians and the Romans, all the big guys, but eventually ended up controlled by the Ottomans.",
    "confidence": 0.8885,
    "speakerId": 1,
